<title>wjhk nʿạyn bhtạf</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- wjhk nʿạyn bhtạf bạlbr nrạh wnslk bnwrh
 yạ yswʿ ạlmsyḥ yạ ạbn ạllh yạ wjh ạlnwr yạ bhạʾ ạllh
 yạ lḥḍrh ạlbhyẗ yạ nwr ạlbryẗ
 2- wjhk lạ tḥjb ạ̉bdạ ʿnạ wjhk yạrb nṭlb fạ̉ʿnạ
 3- wjhk yhrb mn ạ̉mạmh mbgẖḍwk wttrḍạh ạlsẖʿwb bhdyẗ
 4- wjhk ttqdmẗ ạlrḥmẗ wạlạ̉mạnẗ ybṣrh mn ʿạsẖ lk bạlạ̹stqạmẗ
 5- wjhk nṭlbh fy ḍyqạtnạ tstrnạ bstrh mn mkạyd ạlnạs
 6- wjhk ysyr ạ̉mạmnạ fyryḥnạ ynyr ʿlynạ fnkẖlṣ</lyrics>
</song>